"system2"="Settings\n\nIn Agnes everything is a note, even settings.\n\nChange the values below to your liking:\n\nCOLORS\n\nbarTintColor={$agnes-barTintColor}\n(navigation bar color)\n\ntintColor={$agnes-tintColor}\n(highlight and icons color)\n\nFONT\n\nfontName={$agnes-fontName}\n(font name)\n\nfontSize={$agnes-fontSize}\n(font size in points, from 8 to 28)\n\ndynamicType={$agnes-dynamicType}\n(override font with device Settings)\n\nOTHER\n\nstatusBarHidden={$agnes-statusBarHidden}\n\nUse the word default to restore a setting to its original value.";
